description:
Admission control parameters for various cells in a 5G network.

- dateTime: Timestamp of the admission control configuration.
- Area_Name: Geographic area of the cell.
- CellId: Unique identifier of the cell (eNodeB/gNB).
- Id2: Duplicate of CellId.
- Id3:  Likely an internal identifier, seemingly always '1' in this sample.
- vsDataType: Data type identifier, indicating admission control data.
- vsDataFormatVersion: Version of the data format.
- AdmissionControl.rrcMcsPriorityAccessPrio: Priority for RRC connection establishment using MCS.
- AdmissionControl.rrcReestablishmentPrio: Priority for RRC reestablishment.
- AdmissionControl.admissionPrioThreshold: Threshold for admission priority.
- AdmissionControl.rrcRnaUpdatePrio: Priority for RRC NAS update.
- AdmissionControl.rrcMoVideoCallPrio: Priority for originating video calls.
- AdmissionControl.rrcMtAccessPrio: Priority for terminating access.
- AdmissionControl.rrcMoSignalingPrio: Priority for originating signaling.
- AdmissionControl.rrcMoVoiceCallPrio: Priority for originating voice calls.
- AdmissionControl.rrcEmergencyPrio: Priority for emergency calls.
- AdmissionControl.rrcMoSmsPrio: Priority for originating SMS messages.
- AdmissionControl.rrcHighPriorityAccessPrio: Priority for high-priority access.
- AdmissionControl.rrcMoDataPrio: Priority for originating data.
- AdmissionControl.admissionControlId: Unique ID for this admission control configuration.
- AdmissionControl.rrcMpsPriorityAccessPrio: Priority for RRC connection establishment using MPS.
- AdmissionControl.admNrRrcDifferentiationThr: Differentiation threshold for NR RRC in Admission Control.
- AdmissionControl.admNrRbDifferentiationThr: Differentiation threshold for NR RB in Admission Control.
- AdmissionControl.arpBasedPreEmptionState: State of ARP-based preemption.
- AdmissionControl.limitSrNonPa: Limit on SR non-PA.
- AdmissionControl.preemptInactTimerMin: Minimum preemption inactivity timer.
- AdmissionControl.dlMbmsGbrRatio: Ratio of MBMS GBR in downlink.
- AdmissionControl.resourceReservationForPAState: State of resource reservation for priority access.
- AdmissionControl.nrOfRbReservationsPerPaConn: Number of RB reservations per PA connection.
- AdmissionControl.nrOfPaConnHpaReservPerCell: Number of PA connection HPA reservations per cell.
- AdmissionControl.dlAdmDifferentiationThr: Downlink admission differentiation threshold.
- AdmissionControl.paArpOverrideHpa: PA ARP override for HPA.
- AdmissionControl.nrOfPrevPreempPaRbReservation: Number of previously preempted PA RB reservations.
- AdmissionControl.dlTransNwBandwidth: Downlink transport network bandwidth.
- AdmissionControl.lbAtoThresholdLevel2: Load balancing ATO threshold level 2.
- AdmissionControl.lbAtoThresholdLevel1: Load balancing ATO threshold level 1.

- AdmissionControl.admResourceMinQciPrio: Minimum QCI priority for admission control resource.
